description: Asfour is the most famous crystal chandeliers in Egypt, there is a vast array to choose from. The hundreds of shining lights and glittering crystals in the showroom make it a magical space, worth seeing even if you don't purchase anything. beside the huge selection of chandeliers and other light fittings, there is a jewelry, 3D laser gifts, and figurines, helpful and knowledgeable sales staff...
